data.description: Beautiful  two story home located in desirable Cobblestone Farms. dining room and large living room. The floor plan with one bedroom and one full bathroom on first level is perfect for guests, nursery or home office. Upstairs you'll find four bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, laundry room and a loft. From master bedroom you have mountain view. The beautiful Eat-in kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, window over sink and a breakfast island. Enjoy your backyard oasis with covered patio, grass landscaping and mature trees. Don't miss out on this move-in ready 5 bed/ 3 bath home. Upgrades include complete interior paint, new garage door motor and new microwave.
